name: BlockCity | B02H03 | META-Doughnuts
description:
Eat as many doughnuts as you can without adapting the shape of one? No problem! What started as a social-media company is now the biggest supplier of virtual doughnuts in the galaxy. While the metaverse failed as a platform for social interaction, it never fails your taste and belly. 

Own a 12-second turntable of your 3D-rendered meta real estate - visit BlockCity: https://rtz23.de/blockcity/?b=2
